OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fgradually easing during the evening
OL,7,Fbut lingering for some across southern
OL,8,Fparts of Wales. Remaining largely
OL,9,Fcloudy and generally mild, though
OL,10,Fchillier under any prolonged clear
OL,11,Fspells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cloudy start for many on
OL,14,FMonday. Perhaps a few brighter spells
OL,15,Femerging later. A continued risk of
OL,16,Fshowers in the south. Temperatures
OL,17,Fclose to normal for early May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
